data.description: This well-maintained 2-story home offers four bedrooms and 21/2 baths. All bedrooms and a nice size game room are located on the 2nd floor. Large backyard with aboveground pool that can be taken down or left. Minutes away from shopping and entertainment (Town Lake) with Cyfair schools It is conveniently located near Hwy 290! Can and schedule a showing!
